{"word":"H7936 - שָׂכַר - sâkar - saw-kar' - Earn wages","slug":"H7936","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂכַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sâkar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-kar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Earn wages"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05DB;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05DB;&#x05E8; - s&#x0301;a&#x0302;kar  sa&#x0302;kar</b> - <i>saw-kar', saw-kar'</i><p/>The second form by permutation and used in <a href='B:150 4:5'>Ezr 4:5</a>; a primitive root (apparently akin (by prosthesis) to <a href=\"#/H3739\">H3739</a> through the idea of temporary <i>purchase</i>; compare <a href=\"#/H7937\">H7937</a>); to <i>hire: - </i>earn wages, hire (out self), reward, X surely."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4909\">H4909</a>, <a href=\"#/H7916\">H7916</a>, <a href=\"#/H7917\">H7917</a>, <a href=\"#/H7938\">H7938</a>, <a href=\"#/H7939\">H7939</a>, <a href=\"#/H7940\">H7940</a>, <a href=\"#/H7958\">H7958</a>, <a href=\"#/H8007\">H8007</a>, <a href=\"#/H8009\">H8009</a>, <a href=\"#/H8012\">H8012</a>, <a href=\"#/H8014\">H8014</a>, <a href=\"#/H8073\">H8073</a>"}]}